ent which would soon be named in his honor.  Dreaming that some day i would be in the reigns of such a spectacular legacy.  Little did i know that would soon be the case.<br>
<br>
Deep in the icy night of the Qeynos winter i found myself walking around the courtyard of the Paladin's guild where i was in training to be a holy knight of in the order of Rodcet Nife, when in a dark alley i heard the sounds of a struggle, followed by a dull thud and the toppling of boxes.  Immediately i froze, not wanting to be seen.  My heart racing i took cover as the assailants ran away from the scene of their horrible crime.<br>
<br>
When it was safe to investigate i made my way over to the lifeless form of a fellow stripped to his night shirt, blood dripping from a gash on his chest.  One look at the amulet around his neck told me who it was - Kane.  On the ground beside him was a rucksack which appeared to be full - curiousity getting the best of me i picked it up to take back to my quarters for further investigation.  <br>
<br>
I got about two steps when i felt a strong arm grab me from behind, and i was hoisted off the ground.  A gruff voice of one of the qeynos gaurdsmen was blaring in my ear - but i was too panicked to fully comprehend what was taking place.<br>
<br>
I felt a sharp pain on the back of my head and everything went black.  To this day i'm not sure on the duration of which i was unconcscience, but i came to in a circular room surrounded by the highest paladins of the order, with grave faces - staring at me crumpled on the floor.<br>
<br>
&quot;Rise to your feet young one.&quot;  Staggering to keep my balance i complied.  &quot;Sir Tabula, you have murdered the heir to the throne of antonica, for this you should be executed.  However, a far greater punishment is your destiny - your fledgling abilities in the clerical arts have been denied, forever more you will be excluded from the radiant grace of our order.  Your exile from our order, and Qeynos begins immediately&quot;  I couldnt speak - how did this happen?  They couldn't honestly believe that i had done this?  &quot;For your previous devotion, you will be granted your life, and the mere items you murdered for.  Begone.&quot;<br>
<br>
With that i was escorted 300 yards from the city, and told if i ever returned i would be killed on sight.  <br>
<br>
These are the events that have landed me in my present situation, poor, hungry, and scared in the bustling vermin infested city of Freeport.  All i want is to go home, and perfect the skills that i've wanted since a young child.<br>
<br>
To survive i've had to learn the dark alley-way mannerisms of the Rogues, the very people i swore to hunt down in what feels like a previous life.  They have taken me in as a kind of un-easy ward - they still distrust me, but on the merit of the rumors of my exile from Qeynos , respect me.  All i have to my name is the pack from Kane, and the blood red armor within.<br>
<br>
The Rogues keep eyeing my armor, and i know if i ever remove it, or my blade - they will swiftly remove it from me.  It is for this reason i am leaving their hideout, i will strike out on my own, to the desert east of freeport.  Building up my skills, and learning my new profession - and hopefully one day find out who is responsible for the murder of Kane, and redeem myself in the eyes of the Paladins of Qeynos. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.showMessage?topicID=830.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.showMessage?topicID=828.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.emailToFriend?topicID=833.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.threadControl?topicID=833.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=833.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=833.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option 